  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 54,
      "chapterTitle": "15",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "831600_54_5108-5311",
          "range": "5108-5311",
          "rangeStart": 5108,
          "rangeEnd": 5311,
          "markText": "斯通纳知道——而且很早就知道，他认为——女儿属于那种极其稀有而且永远那么漂亮可爱的人类中的一员，这种人的道德质地是那么娇柔，必须认真养护和关心，这样它才能称心如意。由于跟这个世界格格不入，它只好生存在一个不可能是自己家园的地方。渴望温柔和安静，它只好以冷漠、麻木和喧闹为食粮。这种天性，即使在陌生和充满敌意、不得已要生存的地方，也没有蛮力击退反对它的残暴势力，只有退缩到一个静谧之地，那里荒凉、狭小而柔静。",
          "colorStyle": 4,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1704963769,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-01-11 17:02:49",
          "chapterUid": 54,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=831600&chapterUid=54&rangeStart=5108&rangeEnd=5311",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a0b329e05cb070a0b0f1092?chapterUid=54&rangeStart=5108&rangeEnd=5311"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "831600_54_11808-11884",
          "range": "11808-11884",
          "rangeStart": 11808,
          "rangeEnd": 11884,
          "markText": "斯通纳看着他们驱车离开家，仍然觉得女儿是一个曾经在某个已然遥远的房间，坐在自己身边的小女孩，带着严肃的欢乐表情看着他，仍然觉得是一个早就死去的可爱小孩。",
          "colorStyle": 4,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1704963742,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-01-11 17:02:22",
          "chapterUid": 54,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=831600&chapterUid=54&rangeStart=11808&rangeEnd=11884",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a0b329e05cb070a0b0f1092?chapterUid=54&rangeStart=11808&rangeEnd=11884"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 55,
      "chapterTitle": "16",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "831600_55_1139-1204",
          "range": "1139-1204",
          "rangeStart": 1139,
          "rangeEnd": 1204,
          "markText": "他开始意识到，格蕾斯离开哥伦比亚——也许甚至包括她怀孕——其实是想逃离一座监狱，她现在是出于难以抹去的仁慈和温柔的善心才回来看看。",
          "colorStyle": 4,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1704963748,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-01-11 17:02:28",
          "chapterUid": 55,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=831600&chapterUid=55&rangeStart=1139&rangeEnd=1204",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a0b329e05cb070a0b0f1092?chapterUid=55&rangeStart=1139&rangeEnd=1204"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "831600_55_17045-17134",
          "range": "17045-17134",
          "rangeStart": 17045,
          "rangeEnd": 17134,
          "markText": "“我已经在这个大学教了将近四十年书。我不知道，如果我不做一名教师还能干什么。如果我不教书，我也许——”他停顿了下，好像走神了，接着又决然说：“我要感谢你们所有的人，让我来教书。”",
          "colorStyle": 4,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1704948655,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-01-11 12:50:55",
          "chapterUid": 55,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=831600&chapterUid=55&rangeStart=17045&rangeEnd=17134",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a0b329e05cb070a0b0f1092?chapterUid=55&rangeStart=17045&rangeEnd=17134"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 51,
      "chapterTitle": "12",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "831600_51_530-574",
          "range": "530-574",
          "rangeStart": 530,
          "rangeEnd": 574,
          "markText": "他已经四十二岁，往前，看不到任何自己渴望享受的东西，往后，看不到任何值得费心记住的事物。",
          "colorStyle": 4,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1704963633,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-01-11 17:00:33",
          "chapterUid": 51,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=831600&chapterUid=51&rangeStart=530&rangeEnd=574",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a0b329e05cb070a0b0f1092?chapterUid=51&rangeStart=530&rangeEnd=574"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "831600_51_10207-10297",
          "range": "10207-10297",
          "rangeStart": 10207,
          "rangeEnd": 10297,
          "markText": "四十三岁那年，斯通纳学会了别人——比他年轻的人——在他之前早就学会的东西：你最初爱的那个人并不是你最终爱的那个人，爱不是最终目标而是一个过程，借助这个过程，一个人想去了解另一个人。",
          "colorStyle": 4,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1704948610,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-01-11 12:50:10",
          "chapterUid": 51,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=831600&chapterUid=51&rangeStart=10207&rangeEnd=10297",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a0b329e05cb070a0b0f1092?chapterUid=51&rangeStart=10207&rangeEnd=10297"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 46,
      "chapterTitle": "7",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "831600_46_3521-3607",
          "range": "3521-3607",
          "rangeStart": 3521,
          "rangeEnd": 3607,
          "markText": "斯通纳跟母亲争辩了会儿，但她不为所动。他终于意识到，她只想等着死，想在她曾经生活的地方死去。他知道，母亲还维护着那个小小的尊严，当她想这样做时在这个过程中能找到的那份尊严。",
          "colorStyle": 4,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1704963520,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-01-11 16:58:40",
          "chapterUid": 46,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=831600&chapterUid=46&rangeStart=3521&rangeEnd=3607",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a0b329e05cb070a0b0f1092?chapterUid=46&rangeStart=3521&rangeEnd=3607"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 44,
      "chapterTitle": "5",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "831600_44_1218-1341",
          "range": "1218-1341",
          "rangeStart": 1218,
          "rangeEnd": 1341,
          "markText": "不出一个月，斯通纳就知道自己的婚姻失败了。不到一年，他已经不抱改善的希望。他学会了沉默，不再固执地去爱。如果他要跟伊迪丝说话，或者在温柔的冲动下想抚摸，她就躲开，沉溺在自己的内心里，变得沉默寡言，强忍着，然后会连续好几天强迫自己达到新的疲惫极限。",
          "colorStyle": 4,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1704963463,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-01-11 16:57:43",
          "chapterUid": 44,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=831600&chapterUid=44&rangeStart=1218&rangeEnd=1341",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a0b329e05cb070a0b0f1092?chapterUid=44&rangeStart=1218&rangeEnd=1341"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
